snippet.title: Chainmail Bikini Release Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Chainmail Bikini is an RPGMaker game that follows the adventures of a hero named Brandi the Red and her companions as they hunt monsters for fun and profit. Available now on Steam at https://store.steampowered.com/app/2229050/Chainmail_Bikini/

Cover image by Dean Spencer Art https://www.patreon.com/deanspencerart/
Music by Alexander Nakarada https://www.patreon.com/anakarada

For more news, info, and to support my work visit https://www.patreon.com/TravisLegge
